      <title>[인사] 국무조정실·총리비서실 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/11/16/CWQHDC5D6VFMXB6I7OXJ3SEURY/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/11/16/CWQHDC5D6VFMXB6I7OXJ3SEURY/</guid>
